/wiki/To_Hon_To: To Hon To ( , born 4 April 1989 ) is a Hong Kong professional football player playing for Hong Kong First Division club South China . His position is forward .
/wiki/Kitchee_SC: Kitchee Sports Club ( Chinese : 傑志體育會 ; Jyutping : Git6zi3 Tai2juk6wui2 ; [ kìːt̚ tsīː tʰɐ̌i jòk̚ wǔːy ] ; pinyin : Jiézhì tǐyù huì ) is a Hong Kong football team based in Kowloon . It was founded in 1931 and currently competes in the Hong Kong Premier League . The club has won the Hong Kong Premier League three times , the Hong Kong First Division six times , and the Hong Kong FA Cup four times in their history . In the last 5 years , Kitchee won slightly more than 50% of all possible trophies being competed in Hong Kong .
/wiki/Tai_Po_FC: Tai Po Football Club ( ) , currently known as Wofoo Tai Po due to sponsorship reasons , is a Hong Kong professional football club currently competing in the Hong Kong Premier League . The club is formed by the Tai Po District Council .
/wiki/Aender_Naves_Mesquita: Aender Naves Mesquita ( commonly known as Naves , ; born 12 February 1983 in Barra do Garças , Mato Grosso , Brazil ) , is a Brazilian-born Hong Kong footballer who currently plays for Hong Kong Premier League club Rangers .
/wiki/South_China_AA: South China Athletic Association ( also known as South China , SCAA , Chinese : 南華體育會 ) is a football club which currently competes in the Hong Kong First Division , the second-level league in Hong Kong football league system . The club has won a record 41 First Division titles , a record 31 Senior Shields , a record 10 FA Cups and 3 League Cups . Nicknamed Shaolin Temple and Caroliners , South China has produced many great Hong Kong footballers over the years . In November 2007 , the club entered into a charity partnership with Hong Kong Red Cross . The partnership is a pioneer between a sports association and a humanitarian organisation in Hong Kong . The club plays most of its home matches at Happy Valley Recreation Ground .
/wiki/Jing_Teng: Jing Teng ( ; born 20 May 1990 in Ma'anshan ) is a Chinese-born Hong Kong footballer who plays for Hong Kong First Division club Wong Tai Sin as a midfielder .
/wiki/Sun_Hei_SC: Sun Hei Sports Club ( Chinese : 晨曦體育會 ) is a Hong Kong football club which currently competes in the Hong Kong Third Division .
/wiki/Li_Hon_Ho: Li Hon Ho ( born on 14 July 1986 in Hong Kong ) , is a Hong Kong professional football player currently playing as a goalkeeper for Hong Kong Premier League club Lee Man .
/wiki/Eastern_AA: Eastern Athletic Association Football Team Limited , also known as Eastern Sports Club ( ) is a Hong Kong professional sports club with football and basketball sections . The football team is known as Eastern Football Team ( ) ( currently known for sponsorship reasons as Eastern Long Lions Football Team ( ) and plays in the Hong Kong Premier League .
/wiki/Clayton_Michel_Afonso: Clayton Michel Afonso ( , born 18 July 1988 in Brazil ) , commonly known simply as Clayton , is a Brazilian born , Hong Kong professional football player who currently plays for Hong Kong Premier League club Eastern .
/wiki/Li_Shu_Yeung: Li Shu Yeung ( , born 2 May 1991 in Hong Kong ) is a professional footballer who currently plays for Hong Kong First Division club South China as a right-back .
/wiki/Yokohama_FC_Hong_Kong: Metro Gallery Football Club ( ) , currently known as Icanfield for sponsorship reasons , are a Hong Kong football club which currently competes in the Hong Kong First Division .
/wiki/Pang_Tsz_Kin: Pang Tsz Kin ( ; born 16 December 1986 ) is a Hong Kong former professional footballer .
/wiki/Happy_Valley_AA: Happy Valley Athletic Association ( ) , known simply as Happy Valley or HVAA , are a Hong Kong football club which currently competes in the Hong Kong Premier League . They are historically one of the most successful football clubs in Hong Kong , having won the First Division six times and had consistently been in the top division , until they were relegated to the Second Division after the 2009-10 season . The club is part of a sports association which also operates swimming , basketball , first aid , table tennis , athletics and various other recreation activities under its umbrella .
/wiki/Wong_Yim_Kwan: Wong Yim Kwan ( ; born 1 August 1992 in Hong Kong ) is a Hong Kong footballer who currently plays for Hong Kong Premier League club Lee Man .
/wiki/Alex_Tayo_Akande: Alexander Oluwatayo Akande ( ; born 9 February 1989 ) , more commonly known as Alex Akande or Alex Tayo Akande , is a Hong Kong footballer who currently plays as a striker for Chinese Super League club Dalian Yifang .
/wiki/Christian_Annan: Christian Kwesi Annan ( ; born ) is a Ghanaian-born Hong Kong professional footballer who currently plays as a striker for Hong Kong Premier League club Rangers . He is renowned in Hong Kong for his high pace and dribbling skill .
/wiki/Che_Runqiu: Che Runqiu ( ; born 25 October 1990 in Guangzhou , China ) , is a Chinese-born Hong Kong footballer who currently plays as a midfielder and defender for Hong Kong Premier League club Tai Po .
/wiki/Southern_District_RSA: Southern District Recreation & Sports Assn Ltd ( Chinese : 南區足球會 ) , commonly known as Southern and currently known for sponsorship reasons as Kwoon Chung Southern , is a professional football club based in Southern District , Hong Kong . They currently compete in the Hong Kong Premier League .
